1364
01:51:35,637 --> 01:51:36,661
Very good...

1365
01:51:36,938 --> 01:51:38,132
...color, sir.

1366
01:51:42,343 --> 01:51:44,072
Smells nice too.

1367
01:51:58,993 --> 01:52:00,984
Very nice little number.

1368
01:52:02,263 --> 01:52:03,594
Here's to it.

1369
01:52:12,307 --> 01:52:14,798
Very refreshing, sir.
Very refreshing.

1370
01:52:15,109 --> 01:52:18,010
I'm pleased you appreciate good wine.

1371
01:52:19,113 --> 01:52:21,013
Have another glass.

1372
01:52:34,195 --> 01:52:35,526
My wife...

1373
01:52:36,998 --> 01:52:40,525
... used to do everything for me
and leave me to my writing.

1374
01:52:43,438 --> 01:52:45,030
Your wife? Is she away?

1375
01:52:45,507 --> 01:52:47,839
She's dead!

1376
01:52:51,913 --> 01:52:53,744
I'm sorry to hear about that, sir.

1377
01:52:54,048 --> 01:52:56,346
