during a flu epidemic.

1383
01:53:12,166 --> 01:53:16,364
The doctors told me it was
pneumonia, but I knew what it was.

1384
01:53:16,671 --> 01:53:21,040
A victim of the modern age.
Poor, poor girl!

1385
01:53:24,979 --> 01:53:26,571
And now you.

1386
01:53:27,181 --> 01:53:30,241
Another victim of the modern age.

1387
01:53:30,552 --> 01:53:32,452
But you can be helped.

1388
01:53:33,488 --> 01:53:36,889
