-Help you.

1393
01:53:43,898 --> 01:53:47,390
-Who are they?
-Very, very important people.

1394
01:53:47,602 --> 01:53:50,002
And they're interested in you.

1395
01:53:55,510 --> 01:53:57,705
Julian. This'll be these people now.

1396
01:53:57,912 --> 01:54:01,313
