any further. I should be leaving.

1397
01:54:02,417 --> 01:54:04,385
No trouble at all.

1398
01:54:05,086 --> 01:54:06,280
Here.

1399
01:54:06,521 --> 01:54:08,421
Let me fill your glass.

1400
01:54:34,148 --> 01:54:35,843
So this is the young man.

1401
01:54:37,251 --> 01:54:38,718
How do you do, sir?

1402
01:54:39,053 --> 01:54:41,715
Missus.
I'm very pleased to meet you.

1403
01:54:42,123 --> 01:54:44,557
I hope you forgive us for coming at this hour...

1404
01:54:44,826 --> 01:54:46,657
... but we heard you were in trouble...

1405
01:54:46,961 --> 01:54:49,225
...and so we came over to see if we could help.

1406
01:54:49,464 --> 01:54:51,762
Very kind of you, sir.
Thank you very much.

1407
01:54:51,966 --> 01:54:54,230
I understand you had a rather...

1408
01:54:54,469 --> 01:54:55,731
... unfortunate...

1409
01:54:55,970 --> 01:54:57,460
...encounter...

1410
01:54:57,739 --> 01:54:59,468
...with the police tonight.

1411
01:54:59,741 --> 01:55:01,766
Yes, I suppose you could call it that.

1412
01:55:02,076 --> 01:55:03,338
How are you feeling now?

1413
01:55:03,645 --> 01:55:04,873
Much better, thank you.

1414
01:55:05,146 --> 01:55:07,478
Feel like talking, answering a few questions?

1415
01:55:07,782 --> 01:55:09,079
Fine, sir. Fine.

1416
01:55:09,951 --> 01:55:12,579
As I said, we've heard about you.

1417
01:55:13,087 --> 01:55:15,783
We are interested in your case.

1418
01:55:15,990 --> 01:55:18,891
-We want to help you.
-Thank you very much, sir.

1419
01:55:19,160 --> 01:55:22,288
Shall we get down to it?

1420
01:55:22,497 --> 01:55:24,294
Fine. Fine, sir.

1421
01:55:29,604 --> 01:55:32,402
The newspapers mentioned...

1422
01:55:32,607 --> 01:55:36,907
...in addition to being conditioned
against acts of sex and violence...

1423
01:55:37,178 --> 01:55:40,511
...you've inadvertently been
conditioned against music.

1424
01:55:41,582 --> 01:55:44,608
I think that was something
that they didn't plan for.

1425
01:55:44,986 --> 01:55:46,886
You see, missus...

1426
01:55:47,121 --> 01:55:50,613
