1439
01:56:30,331 --> 01:56:34,563
And then all I can think about
is, like, trying to snuff it.

1440
01:56:34,869 --> 01:56:39,272
-I beg your pardon?
-Snuff it. Death, I mean.

1441
01:56:39,540 --> 01:56:42,065
I just want to die peacefully...

1442
01:56:42,577 --> 01:56:44,875
...like, with no pain.

1443
01:56:45,680 --> 01:56:47,580
Do you feel that way now?

1444
01:56:48,683 --> 01:56:50,674
No, sir, not exactly.

1445
01:56:50,885 --> 01:56:52,182
I still feel...

1446
01:56:52,386 --> 01:56:53,683
...very miserable.

1447
01:56:53,888 --> 01:56:56,448
Very much down in spirits.

1448
01:56:56,991 --> 01:56:58,288
Do you still feel...

1449
01:56:58,559 --> 01:57:00,049
