terrible is going to happen to me.

1454
01:57:29,323 --> 01:57:30,984
Well done, Frank.

1455
01:57:36,998 --> 01:57:38,795
Julian, get the car, would you, please?

1456
01:57:59,420 --> 01:58:00,751
I woke up...

1457
01:58:06,327 --> 01:58:10,058
