1467
01:58:58,312 --> 01:58:59,210
Stop it!

1468
01:59:47,528 --> 01:59:49,018
Turn it off!

1469
01:59:50,464 --> 01:59:51,431
Please!

1470
01:59:51,666 --> 01:59:53,861
Turn it off!

1471
02:00:07,782 --> 02:00:10,683
