1474
02:00:16,490 --> 02:00:17,889
To snuff it.

1475
02:00:18,259 --> 02:00:21,592
To blast off forever,
out of this wicked, cruel world.

1476
02:00:23,197 --> 02:00:25,597
One moment of pain, perhaps...

1477
02:00:25,900 --> 02:00:27,663
...and then sleep.

1478
02:00:27,902 --> 02:00:30,462
Forever and ever...

1479
02:00:30,705 --> 02:00:32,002
...and ever.

1480
02:00:56,497 --> 02:00:58,226
I jumped, O my brothers...

1481
02:00:58,532 --> 02:00:59,931
...and I fell hard.

1482
02:01:00,201 --> 02:01:02,499
But I did not snuff it.

1483
02:01:03,104 --> 02:01:04,696
If I had snuffed it...

1484
02:01:04,939 --> 02:01:08,306
...I would not be here
to tell what I have told.

1485
02:01:10,144 --> 02:01:14,808
I came back to life
after a long, black, black gap...

1486
02:01:15,049 --> 02:01:18,348
... of what might have been
a million years.

1487
02:01:47,081 --> 02:01:49,641
He's recovered
consciousness, Doctor.

1488
02:02:29,723 --> 02:02:31,213
Hello, lad.

1489
02:02:31,525 --> 02:02:33,015
Hello, son.

1490
02:02:34,028 --> 02:02:35,427
How are you?

1491
02:02:36,630 --> 02:02:38,621
You feeling better?

1492
02:02:43,037 --> 02:02:44,129
What...

1493
02:02:44,338 --> 02:02:45,396
...gives...

1494
02:02:46,841 --> 02:02:48,832
... O my Pee and Em?

1495
02:02:49,743 --> 02:02:51,335
What makes...

1496
02:02:52,113 --> 02:02:53,011
...you think...

1497
02:02:53,314 --> 02:02:55,714
...you are welcome?

1498
02:02:58,652 --> 02:03:00,643
There, there, Mother.
It's all right.

1499
02:03:00,855 --> 02:03:02,516
He doesn't mean it.

1500
02:03:04,959 --> 02:03:07,450
You were in the papers again, son.

1501
02:03:08,262 --> 02:03:09,854
It said...

1502
02:03:10,131 --> 02:03:12,827
...they had done
great wrong to you.

1503
02:03:13,667 --> 02:03:15,032
It said...

1504
02:03:15,336 --> 02:03:16,633
... how the government...

1505
02:03:16,871 --> 02:03:18,862
...drove you to try...

1506
02:03:19,140 --> 02:03:20,664
...and do yourself in.

1507
02:03:22,543 --> 02:03:24,773
And when you think about it, son...

1508
02:03:25,880 --> 02:03:28,542
... maybe it was our fault too...

1509
02:03:28,883 --> 02:03:30,145
...in a way.

1510
02:03:31,252 --> 02:03:33,152
Your home's your home...

1511
02:03:33,487 --> 02:03:36,047
...when all's said and done, son.

1512
